(1) Te deum laudamus (fol. 182r);

(2) Benedicite omnia opera (fol. 183r);

(3) Benedictus dominus deus (fol. 184v);

(4) Magnificat (fol. 185r);

(5) Nunc dimittis (fol. 185v);

(6) Athanasian Creed (Quicumque uult ...) (fol. 186r).
